<h2>Floating UI Adapter</h2>
<p>
    The Floating UI Adapter implements the Web Everything <strong>Positioning Protocol</strong> using the <a href="https://floating-ui.com/">Floating UI</a> library.
</p>

<section class="section-card">
    <h3 id="status">Status</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
        <strong>Concept Phase:</strong> This adapter is in early design.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="section-card">
    <h3 id="concept">Concept</h3>
    <p>
        Floating UI provides robust positioning for tooltips, popovers, dropdowns, and other floating elements. This adapter bridges it to Web Everything's positioning protocol:
    </p>

    {% highlight "typescript" %}
import { FloatingUIAdapter } from '@web-adapters/floating-ui';

// Register the adapter
positioningRegistry.define('floating-ui', FloatingUIAdapter);

// Use in components
<dropdown-menu positioning="floating-ui">
    <button slot="trigger">Open Menu</button>
    <menu-items slot="content">...</menu-items>
</dropdown-menu>
    {% endhighlight %}
</section>

